---
// Import your components
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css'
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | Sergio Ramírez Morón</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-900 font-sans antialiased">
    
    <Header />

    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-24 pb-16">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl mb-8">
            Privacy Policy
        </h1>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
                Last updated: <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">January 2026</span>
            </p>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    Welcome to my portfolio. Your privacy is important. This policy explains how I handle information (which is basically none, as this is a static website).
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. Data I Collect</h2>
                <p>
                    Currently, this website <strong>does not collect personal data</strong> from users. I do not use tracking cookies, registration forms, or invasive analytics.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Third-Party Links</h2>
                <p>
                    My website contains links to external sites such as GitHub or LinkedIn. Please note that I am not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.
                </p>
            </section>
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions about this policy, you can contact me through the methods listed on the homepage.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</body>
</html>
